    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the CFD model is fit for the intended COU despite identified shortfalls in numerical code verification, discretization error quantification, and validation relevance. The team concluded that the output comparison results and engineering judgment provide sufficient confidence. The claim node (https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cpb-hemolysis-claim-orphan) is asserted without traceability to supporting evidence or prior derivation. Three factors achieved levels below their required levels; no compensating measures or risk mitigations were formally documented prior to the Accepted decision.",
